Titolo: Body and Brain Connection

Anno: 2010

Descrizione: Body and Brain Connection, also known as Dr. Kawashima's Body and Brain Exercises in PAL regions, is an puzzle video game developed and published by Namco Bandai Games for the Xbox 360's Kinect platform. It was released in Japan on November 20, 2010, in North America on February 8, 2011, and in Europe on February 11, 2011.
The game features mental problems, such as math questions, in order to keep the user's brain active; in order to answer the questions, the player must perform various physical motions. It received mostly mixed reviews from critics.

Genere: Non specificato


Valutazione: N/A
